		{
			dependencies: ["IV01000000000005"]
			description: ["The Micro Processor Computer represents full mastery of the IV circuit tier. It is the direct recipe input for the most demanding IV machine components and a gate into the Nano Processor tier above. But the circuit ladder alone is not enough to open the next stage — your magical progression must also have reached Elven attainment. The Alfheim Portal and its trade system stand between you and the Nano Processor Mainframe."]
			id: "IV01000000000006"
