		{
			dependencies: [
				"IV01000000000006"
				"4BFCD345F6B88901"
			]
			description: ["Elementium Ingots are smelted from Dragonstone returned through the Alfheim Portal trade system, after Elves accept your mana contributions and send back elemental materials. Elementium Armor's Pixie affinity — each piece procs a Guardian Pixie on damage taken — provides meaningful damage mitigation in sustained combat. Assembling the full set signals that your magical progression has matched your industrial ambition, and the Nano Processor tier opens. The Elves are satisfied. Press on."]
			id: "IV01000000000007"
