		{
			dependencies: ["IV01000000000007"]
			description: ["The Nano Processor Mainframe is the culmination of the IV circuit tier — a bus-sized computational array that serves as both the IV multiblock controller and the input for LuV machine assembly. A fully automated Circuit Assembler running your Nano Processor line is required for practical throughput. Manual crafting produces bottlenecks within minutes of beginning IV machine construction. This milestone marks the transition from EV-scale industry into GTCEu's high-voltage endgame."]
			id: "IV01000000000008"
