		{
			dependencies: ["IV01000000000008"]
			description: ["The IV Circuit Assembler doubles the throughput of the MV version and is required for automated Nano Processor production. It is the machine that makes future machines — without it, IV circuit production is manual and slow. Wire it directly into your AE2 autocrafting network with pattern providers for each circuit tier, then let the network fulfill requests on demand. From this point forward, no circuit is crafted by hand."]
			id: "IV01000000000009"
