		{
			dependencies: ["IV01000000000009"]
			description: ["The IV Parallel Hatch allows multiblock machines to process multiple recipes simultaneously — up to 4 recipe slots per hatch at IV power. Installing it in your Electric Blast Furnace doubles or quadruples throughput with no change to recipe times. Parallel processing is the first true throughput multiplier operating at the multiblock level rather than the component level. Build at least two and install one in your EBF before beginning LuV material production."]
