		{
			dependencies: ["IV01000000000008"]
			description: ["QuarkTech Armor is GTCEu's IV-tier powered suit — constructed from Nano Circuits, Naquadah alloy, and field generation components. Each piece provides solid base defense plus charge slots for EU-powered abilities. The Advanced QuarkTech Chestplate adds flight capability at the cost of continuous EU draw. At IV power, the suit is fully sustainable on a mid-tier battery. This is competitive with Awakened Supremium and replaces the need for Hazmat suits in most non-radioactive environments."]
			id: "IV0100000000000B"
