		{
			dependencies: ["IV01000000000008"]
			description: ["Rhodium-Plated Palladium is the signature LuV material — an exceptionally dense alloy of Palladium with a surface coat of Rhodium applied in the Chemical Reactor. Palladium is extracted from Platinum Group Metal concentrations; Rhodium comes from Palladium ore byproducts. Both require full wet chemistry separation chains in the EBF and Chemical Reactor. This is the material where GTCEu's chemistry tree and its machine tree intersect most tightly — you process one to build the other."]
			id: "IV0100000000000C"
			rewards: [
