		}
		{
			dependencies: ["IV0100000000000C"]
			description: ["Ruridit is an alloy of Iridium and Osmium, processed in the Alloy Smelter at LuV temperature. Osmium is a radioactive heavy metal requiring Hazmat protection during processing. Ruridit provides the structural component for LuV machine frames and the Assembly Line's core construction. It also appears in LuV Scanner and high-tier wiring recipes. Build your Ruridit stock alongside your Rhodium-Plated Palladium run — they are consumed together in LuV Hull and Assembly Line construction."]
			id: "IV0100000000000D"
