			dependencies: [
				"IV0100000000000C"
				"IV0100000000000D"
			]
			description: ["The LuV Machine Hull marks the start of GTCEu's post-IV tier — a region where voltage requirements outpace conventional power generation and research-locked recipes become the norm. The Hull is assembled from Rhodium-Plated Palladium, Ruridit, and LuV circuit boards. From this point, every major machine requires the Assembly Line as its production method. If you have not yet built an Assembly Line, the LuV Hull is the gate — nothing significant advances past this point without one."]
