		{
			dependencies: [
				"IV0100000000000E"
				"IV0100000000000D"
			]
			description: ["The Assembly Line is GTCEu's most important multiblock. It accepts multi-ingredient sequential recipes that no other machine can perform and is the sole production method for all LuV+ machines, sensors, emitters, and circuit assemblies. Research Items are submitted via a Research Station and stored in the Data Bank, then inserted via the data input hatch. Plan your first Assembly Line build carefully — the space requirement, maintenance inputs, and research infrastructure demand significant preparation."]
