		{
			dependencies: ["IV01000000000010"]
			description: ["The LuV Sensor is used in Assembly Line recipes for higher machines and as a component in Quantum circuit assemblies. Sensors at the LuV tier contain Ruridit and Quantum CPU elements — expensive but consumed infrequently. Build a buffer of 16–32 units before beginning any sustained LuV production run. The Sensor also enables the LuV Scanner, which is your gateway into the Research Station loop."]
