		{
			dependencies: ["IV01000000000011"]
			description: ["The LuV Scanner is a consumable tool used to produce Research Items for submission to the Research Station. Each unique Assembly Line recipe requires a corresponding Research Item to unlock — scanning new items adds them to your recipe database. Keep a powered Scanner adjacent to your Research Station at all times; the research loop blocks Assembly Line output if the Data Bank is missing a required recipe."]
