		{
			dependencies: ["IV01000000000010"]
			description: ["The Data Bank stores Research Items produced by the Research Station and makes them accessible to the Assembly Line's data input hatch network. A single Data Bank can hold a large number of recipe entries. Keep it under passive power at all times — losing power to the Data Bank mid-run pauses Assembly Line production until the data connection is restored. Install it in your multiblock room's power grid, not on a separate circuit."]
